These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, italian, argentine, chinese
There 4 different types of food: pear, kiwi, spinach, garlic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, dahlia, poppy
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the person who growsazalea##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsazalea is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 7. the italian is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 8. the person eating garlic is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who growstulip##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person eating spinach##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the chinese##1
11. the argentine is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
12. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
13. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the italian is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the italian is not the person who growstulip##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality         | nigerian     | italian   | chinese | argentine |
| Food   | kiwi | garlic   | pear   | spinach  |
| Flower         | tulip  | dahlia  | poppy  | azalea |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

