.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game, tiparillo, prince
House: farmhouse, futuristic, modern, victorian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, librarian, videographer, security-guard
 1. the fan of salsa is between the architect and the fan of indie##2
 2. the game-smoker is not to the right of the librarian##8
 3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 4. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the security-guard##8
 5. the architect is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the victorian house is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
 7. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
 8. the videographer is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the librarian##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the architect##3
11. the architect is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the prince-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the modern house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
17. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the futuristic house is not to the right of the librarian##8
19. the prince-smoker is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Cigar      | bongani | tiparillo | prince  | game  |
| House          | victorian     | futuristic | farmhouse | modern  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Job           | videographer | security-guard | architect    | librarian  |

