.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, lizard, ferret
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, pomegranate, grapes
4 different games are played: domino, chess, mah-jongg, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
 6. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the person eating pomegranate##8
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
12. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret   | lizard | fish |
| Food   | asparagus     | pomegranate  | grapes   | blueberry      |
| Game   | chess | domino    | mah-jongg      | canasta       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

