 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 6. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the malaysian##1
10. the italian is the person who likes yellow##1
11. the person who likes orange is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
12. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the italian is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

