 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 5. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 7. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 8. the malaysian is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
10. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the owner of the rat##8
11. the person who likes lilac is between the person who's birthday is in july and the owner of the chinchilla##2
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
14. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
