 2. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the owner of the hamster##6
 8. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating broccoli##5
10. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
11. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
12. the person eating broccoli is not the owner of the goat##6
13. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the right of the person eating broccoli##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
