15. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
16. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Sport           | weightlifting | skateboarding       | skiing      | ice-hockey  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | martial-arts | western   | drama   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | milk          | 7up      | mirinda  |
| Cigar   | swisher   | fonseca      | oliveros | bluemaster |

